        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-11-25 12:54:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI should have added, if we log at info level in the code, we can never dial it back so maybe it's better to do it like this.",
        "patchset_number": 3
